        <description>指令如下，这是我目前找到的最优雅，最快速的方法： nmcli connection modify eth0 \ ipv4.dns 192.168.31.199 \ ipv4.method manual \ ipv4.gateway 192.168.31.199 \ connection.autoconnect yes nmcli c up eth0 nmcli connection modify eth0 \ ipv4.addresses 192.168.23.60/24 \ ipv4.dns 192.168.23.65 \ ipv4.method manual \ ipv4.gateway 192.168.23.65 \ connection.autoconnect yes nmcli c up eth0 # 访问</description>
